      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="1908_AS_RBH_1_00024"/>Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb895" type="place">Strobl</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51516">Hotel am See</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb429">Salzka<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>ergut</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1908_AS_RBH_1_00023"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb969">Tirol</rs>: Partie in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb988">Seis a. Schlern</rs>, 1000m. N. d. <rs type="work" ref="#pmb51884" subtype="implied">Aquarell</rs> v. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb27687">F. A. C. M<unclear>.</unclear> Reisch</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43520">Meran</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1908_AS_RBH_1_00024"/>Herzliche Grüße. Uns geht es hier und gefällt’s hier
               weiter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr gut. Seit <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01784-1"/><date>10.</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01784-1"><ref target="1908-07-10" type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="See"/>. </note> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t
                  <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10986">Brahm</rs> da.<note xml:id="Fn1908-07-20-01_01" type="footnote"><p>und grüsst herzlich.</p></note> Wir denken bis <date>zweite Hälfte Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date> zu bleiben. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> Rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e. Wohin unbe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ti<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t.
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb44311"><hi rend="latintype">Martino</hi></rs>? <rs type="place" ref="#pmb427"><hi rend="latintype">Campiglio</hi></rs>? <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1061"><hi rend="latintype">Engadin</hi></rs>? – Schreiben Sie recht bald, wie’s Ihnen geht und was Sie <pb facs="1908_AS_RBH_1_00023"/>treiben.</p><closer>Von Herzen Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb2173"/>Herzliche Grüsse!</p><closer><signed>OlgaS.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
